# LamImager 简略架构图

> 每个节点标注 `[详细架构映射: ...]` 指向 architecture-detail.mmd 中的对应子图/节点

## 简略架构总览

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph FE["前端 Vue3 SPA<br/>[详细架构映射: FRONTEND]"]
        direction TB
        Views["8个页面视图<br/>Sessions(核心) + 7个管理页<br/>[详细架构映射: F_VIEWS]"]
        Components["4个共享组件<br/>AgentStreamCard/CheckpointOverlay<br/>ConfirmDialog/ErrorBoundary<br/>[详细架构映射: F_COMPONENTS]"]
        Stores["3个Pinia Store<br/>session/provider/billing<br/>[详细架构映射: F_STORES]"]
        API["12个API客户端模块<br/>REST(Axios) + SSE(fetch)<br/>[详细架构映射: F_API]"]
        Composables["4个Composable<br/>useSessionEvents/useDialog<br/>useMarkdown/useDownload<br/>[详细架构映射: F_COMPOSABLES]"]
    end

    subgraph COMM["通信协议层<br/>[详细架构映射: COMMUNICATION]"]
        REST["REST API<br/>59个端点<br/>Axios → /api/*"]
        SSE["SSE 流式<br/>4个流式端点<br/>fetch + parseSSEStream"]
    end

    subgraph BE["后端 FastAPI<br/>[详细架构映射: BACKEND]"]
        direction TB
        Routers["11个路由模块<br/>59个API端点<br/>[详细架构映射: B_ROUTERS]"]
        Services["16个服务模块<br/>核心: generate/agent<br/>intent/plan_execution<br/>支撑: session/billing/api_mgr<br/>settings/skill/rule/ref<br/>plan_template/prompt_opt<br/>task_manager/agent_bridge<br/>[详细架构映射: B_SERVICES]"]
        Tools["4个Agent工具<br/>web_search/image_search<br/>generate_image/plan<br/>+ ToolRegistry单例<br/>[详细架构映射: B_TOOLS]"]
        Utils["3个工具库<br/>crypto(AES-256-GCM)<br/>llm_client(OpenAI兼容)<br/>image_client(3层回退)<br/>[详细架构映射: B_UTILS]"]
        Core["事件系统<br/>LamEvent + EventLog<br/>[详细架构映射: B_CORE]"]
        Models["9个数据模型<br/>Session/Message/Billing<br/>Provider/Skill/Rule<br/>Reference/PlanTemplate<br/>AppSetting<br/>[详细架构映射: B_MODELS]"]
    end

    subgraph EXT["外部服务<br/>[详细架构映射: EXTERNAL]"]
        LLM["LLM API<br/>OpenAI兼容"]
        IMG["图像生成API<br/>OpenAI兼容"]
        SERPER["Serper API<br/>搜索服务"]
        DB["SQLite<br/>lamimager.db"]
    end

    Views -->|Pinia| Stores
    Views -->|composable| Composables
    Views -->|component| Components
    Views -->|API调用| API
    Stores -->|REST/SSE| API

    API -->|REST| Routers
    API -->|SSE| Routers
    Composables -->|SSE| Routers

    Routers -->|调用| Services
    Services -->|调用| Services
    Services -->|registry.get| Tools
    Services -->|调用| Utils
    Services -->|SQLAlchemy| Models
    Services -->|publish/subscribe| Core

    Tools -->|HTTP| SERPER
    Tools -->|调用| Services
    Utils -->|HTTP POST| LLM
    Utils -->|HTTP POST| IMG
    Models -->|aiosqlite| DB

    classDef fe fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1565C0,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    classDef comm fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#2E7D32,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    classDef be fill:#FFF3E0,stroke:#E65100,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    classDef ext fill:#F3E5F5,stroke:#6A1B9A,stroke-width:2px,color:#000

    class FE fe
    class COMM comm
    class BE be
    class EXT ext
```

