## 简略Agent系统

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Input["用户输入<br/>agent_mode=true"] --> Intent["意图解析<br/>LLM意图分类<br/>[详细架构映射: 意图解析优先级图]"]

    Intent --> Single["single<br/>单图生成"]
    Intent --> Parallel["parallel<br/>多图并行"]
    Intent --> Iterative["iterative<br/>迭代精修"]
    Intent --> Radiate["radiate<br/>辐射套图"]

    Single --> Direct["generate_images_core<br/>直接生图"]
    Parallel --> MultiExec["ParallelExecutor<br/>并行工具调用"]
    Iterative --> IterSteps["IterativeExecutor<br/>顺序执行"]
    Radiate --> RadParams["RadiateExecutor<br/>锚点网格→裁切→扩展"]

    Direct --> Core["3层img2img回退<br/>[详细架构映射: 图片生成3层回退图]"]
    MultiExec --> Core
    IterSteps --> Core
    RadParams --> AnchorGrid["锚点网格→裁切→扩展<br/>[详细架构映射: 辐射策略详细流程图]"]

    Core --> Result["结果验证+消息存储"]

    Input --> AgentLoop["Agent循环<br/>run_agent_loop(max_rounds=5)<br/>[详细架构映射: Agent事件流详细图]"]
    AgentLoop --> LLM["LLM Function Calling"]
    LLM --> ToolCall["工具调用"]
    ToolCall --> WebSearch["web_search"]
    ToolCall --> ImageSearch["image_search"]
    ToolCall --> GenImage["generate_image<br/>(checkpoint=true)"]
    ToolCall --> PlanTool["plan"]

    AgentLoop --> Events["事件广播<br/>[详细架构映射: SSE事件广播详细图]"]
    Events --> SSE["SSE → 前端"]

    classDef intent fill:#FFCDD2,stroke:#C62828,stroke-width:2px
    classDef strategy fill:#E1BEE7,stroke:#6A1B9A,stroke-width:2px
    classDef core fill:#C8E6C9,stroke:#2E7D32,stroke-width:2px
    classDef tool fill:#FFF9C4,stroke:#F57F17,stroke-width:2px
    classDef event fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1565C0,stroke-width:2px

    class Intent intent
    class Single,Parallel,Iterative,Radiate strategy
    class Direct,MultiExec,IterSteps,RadParams,Core,AnchorGrid core
    class WebSearch,ImageSearch,GenImage,PlanTool tool
    class Events,SSE event
```

## 简略安全架构

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph 安全防护层
        SSRF["SSRF防护<br/>/api/images/proxy<br/>1.URL scheme校验(http/https)<br/>2.DNS解析→阻止私有IP<br/>3.Content-Type=image/*"]
        PathTraversal["路径遍历防护<br/>/api/download/image<br/>1.文件名正则白名单<br/>2.is_relative_to()校验"]
        XSS["XSS防护<br/>useMarkdown<br/>1.HTML实体转义<br/>2.过滤危险协议链接<br/>3.外部链接rel=noopener"]
        Crypto["API Key加密<br/>crypto.py<br/>1.机器指纹(MAC+主机名)<br/>2.SHA256派生AES-256密钥<br/>3.AES-256-GCM加密存储<br/>4.响应掩码****5678"]
        Input["输入校验<br/>1.日期ISO格式验证<br/>2.文件名正则白名单<br/>3.URL scheme+DNS校验"]
    end

    classDef security fill:#FFEBEE,stroke:#C62828,stroke-width:2px
    class SSRF,PathTraversal,XSS,Crypto,Input security
```

